stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> LoggedOut
    LoggedOut --> Authenticating : Submit credentials
    Authenticating --> AuthFailed : Invalid credentials
    AuthFailed --> LoggedOut
    Authenticating --> LoggedIn : JWT issued
    LoggedIn --> TokenExpiring : Access token expires
    TokenExpiring --> Refreshing : Auto-refresh
    Refreshing --> LoggedIn : New token
    Refreshing --> LoggedOut : Refresh failed
    LoggedIn --> LoggedOut : Logout clicked
    LoggedOut --> [*]